file=Brand Studio/kai/custom/brand-context/assets/brand-context-template.md · [na:[Brand Name] Analytical Context — TEMPLATE=> One per brand at kai's config `brand_context_path`. Built from REAL facts and instrumented\n> numbers only; unmeasured KPIs are listed as "not yet instrumented," never estimated.\n> Every baseline carries date + source; entries older than the refresh cadence are suspect.\n> Updates append-only. Contradictions with live data (or with weave's arc / echo's narrative)\n> escalate to the operator.\n\n**Brand:** [name] \· **Last full refresh:** [YYYY-MM-DD] \· **Refresh cadence:** [monthly typical]\n · 1a(:1. Audience (who actually buys — from data, not aspiration)=[Segments with evidence: source data, size, behavior. As of dates.]\n · 2p(:2. Positioning (one paragraph)=[Consistent with weave's arc §4 and echo's narrative — cross-check on each refresh.]\n · 3mm:3. Model mechanics (operator-supplied)=- Revenue shape: [AOV / subscription / project-based …] \· Purchase frequency: [ ]\n- Margin shape: [ ] \· Sales cycle: [ ]\n · tb=\| KPI \| Baseline \| As of \| Source \| Notes \| · tb=\|---\|---\|---\|---\|---\| · tb=\| [weekly signups] \| \| \| [GA4 / platform] \| \| · tb=\| [CAC by channel] \| \| \| \| \| · tb=\| [conversion rate] \| \| \| \| \| · tb=\| [NSM + guardrails] \| \| \| [vista's definition; kai measures] \| \| · tb=\| [not yet instrumented: …] \| — \| — \| → instrumentation queue \| \| · 5s&:5. Seasonality & context notes (dated)=[Known cycles, one-off events that distort comparisons — each dated.]\n · tb=\| Date \| KPI \| Old → New \| Why \| · tb=\|---\|---\|---\|---\| · tb=\| Date \| File said / data says \| Escalated \| Resolution \| · tb=\|---\|---\|---\|---\|